foo <- FIBER_TYPES %>%

  mutate(plots = map(.x = data, .f = fiber_donut_chart),

                               sprintf("fiber_count_%s_%s_%s.pdf",

map2(.x = foo$file_name, .y = foo$plots, 
     .f = ~ ggsave(filename = .x, plot = .y, 
                   height = 2, width = 1.3,
                   family = "ArialMT"))
